      "content": "Mission Control to Rover Autonomy Engine. Telemetry packet 77-alpha received. We're seeing significant battery degradation in the primary cells. Please run a diagnostic on the current power levels and prepare the final batch of geological survey data for transmission. We need a status report on how much mission time is left before we have to initiate the scheduled deep sleep protocol to preserve the hardware.",
